snippet.title: Namachuukei 68 (Sharp X68000) - Intro
snippet.description: Reuploading this intro movie in higher quality than previously available. This is the intro cinematic for Namachuukei 68, a Konami computer baseball game for the Sharp X68000, released 1991.
